        <text>
            <body>
                <p>Ego <persName key="d1e11668" xml:id="d1e130590">Haymo</persName>,
                        archidiaconus <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284217" xml:id="d1e130593" corresp="abbaye Saint-Pierre et Saint-Prix de Flavigny">Flaviniacensis</orgName>, notum facio omnibus presentes <lb n="2" />
                        inspecturis quod <persName key="d1e11674" xml:id="d1e130598">Robertus</persName> major de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324421" xml:id="d1e130601" corresp="Bussy-le-Grand (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Buxeio</placeName> dedit Deo et ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e130605" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">Fonte<lb n="3" break="no" />neti</orgName> pro remedio anime sue et antecessorum suorum in
                        perpetuam elemosinam omnia <lb n="4" /> que habebat in decimis de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324446" xml:id="d1e130612" corresp="Ampilly-les-Bordes (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Ampilleio</placeName> et tres
                        denarios censuales in fossato <lb n="5" /> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324994" xml:id="d1e130617" corresp="Ranis">Ranis</placeName>. Hanc elemosinam laudavit uxor sua
                        Bonamia, de cujus capi<lb n="6" break="no" />te erat et filii eorum <persName key="d1e11680" xml:id="d1e130623">Milo</persName>, <persName key="d1e11686" xml:id="d1e130626">Andreas</persName> et <persName key="d1e11693" xml:id="d1e130629">
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">Radulfus</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">Radulphus</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </persName>. Laudavit autem hoc <lb n="7" /> totum <persName key="d1e11699" xml:id="d1e130638">Robertus</persName>, miles, cognomento <persName key="d1e11705" xml:id="d1e130641">
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">Saccus</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">Sacus</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </persName>, de cujus feodo erat. Dedit etiam <lb n="8" /> supradictus
                            <persName key="d1e11711" xml:id="d1e130651">Robertus</persName> predicte
                        ecclesie unum denarium censualem in prato <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324996" xml:id="d1e130654" corresp="Rigo, Rigos">
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">Rigo</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">Rigos</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </placeName> et <lb n="9" /> obolum unum in prato <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324979" xml:id="d1e130663" corresp="Poet">
                            <foreign>Poet</foreign>
                        </placeName>. Et ut hoc ratum sit, ad peticionem ipsius <persName key="d1e11717" xml:id="d1e130667">Roberti</persName>
                        <lb n="10" /> presenti scripto sigillum meum apposui. <app>
                            <lem wit="#A">Actum est hoc</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B" type="omission" />
                        </app> anno gratie <num>m° cc° x°</num>.</p>
                
